Blood, Respondent, v. Kane, Appellant. (Supreme Court, General Term, Fifth Department. June 22, 1889.) For hearing on appeal, see 6 N. Y. Supp. 353.

Argued before Barker, P. J., and Dwight and Maoomber, JJ.

No opinion. Motion for reargument denied; leave to appeal to the court of appeals granted.
